OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain. Becoming drier with
OL,7,Fbright spells for a time in the
OL,8,Fafternoon, best of these in the east.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FMostly cloudy with a little
OL,11,Frain at times, especially over the
OL,12,FSouthwest. Some drier spells too, the
OL,13,Fodd clear interval in the east.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,16,Frain at times, though parts of the
OL,17,Feast coast will stay dry. Some heavier
OL,18,Frain later in the evening, with strong
OL,19,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
